{"type": "article", "id": 15529, "title": "“交错”灯具", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-25T06:30:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135740o2zIpfthJ1eaUTwu.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自台湾的设计工作室 viichendesign，设计了一组名为“交错”的灯具。三盏不同形状的半透明灯相互重叠，犹如墨色的深浅变化，营造出古典的意境。其实，灯具的表面是由建筑工地的金属网做的，灯源安装在屏风后，通过过滤网分散灯光，所以看上去有些像幽静的月光。此外，每个灯座有四条腿支撑，它们的位置都可随意调整。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142616afD3u5nhoxZAY7Rc.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"543\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66381418\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142617f2FDvxqHon0Al4bd.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"543\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66381418\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142617zy7LC6VOkDhYNWZq.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"544\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142618HI5n7jG0yOtJ1zYr.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"543\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66381418\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142618NR2MDWK1nfvbA7sm.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"819\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.00122249\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}